  "date": "2026-02-13",
  "notes": "<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:normal\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\">aCorruption Risk Mapping<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:normal\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\">Interview Report<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\n\n<table class=\"MsoNormalTable\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\n <tbody><tr>\n  <td style=\"border:solid #E6E6E6 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:solid #E6E6E6 .75pt;\n  background:whitesmoke;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt\">\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:normal\"><b><span style=\"color:black;\n  mso-color-alt:windowtext\">Item</span><o:p></o:p></b></p>\n  </td>\n  <td style=\"border:solid #E6E6E6 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:solid #E6E6E6 .75pt;\n  background:whitesmoke;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt\">\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:normal\"><b><span style=\"color:black;\n  mso-color-alt:windowtext\">Information</span><o:p></o:p></b></p>\n  </td>\n </tr>\n <tr>\n  <td style=\"border:solid #E6E6E6 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:solid #E6E6E6 .75pt;\n  background:whitesmoke;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt\">\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:normal\"><b><span style=\"color:black;\n  mso-color-alt:windowtext\">Date of the interview</span><o:p></o:p></b></p>\n  </td>\n  <td style=\"border:solid #E6E6E6 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:solid #E6E6E6 .75pt;\n  padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt\">\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:normal\">13 February 2026<o:p></o:p></p>\n  </td>\n </tr>\n <tr>\n  <td style=\"border:solid #E6E6E6 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:solid #E6E6E6 .75pt;\n  background:whitesmoke;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt\">\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:normal\"><b><span style=\"color:black;\n  mso-color-alt:windowtext\">Interviewee name</span><o:p></o:p></b></p>\n  </td>\n  <td style=\"border:solid #E6E6E6 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:solid #E6E6E6 .75pt;\n  padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt\">\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:normal\"><b>Milan Zelený</b><o:p></o:p></p>\n  </td>\n </tr>\n <tr>\n  <td style=\"border:solid #E6E6E6 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:solid #E6E6E6 .75pt;\n  background:whitesmoke;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt\">\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:normal\"><b><span style=\"color:black;\n  mso-color-alt:windowtext\">Interviewee position</span><o:p></o:p></b></p>\n  </td>\n  <td style=\"border:solid #E6E6E6 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:solid #E6E6E6 .75pt;\n  padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt\">\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:normal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">Country Manager Czech Republic – Europlasma\n  &amp; Amber Plasma<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n  </td>\n </tr>\n <tr>\n  <td style=\"border:solid #E6E6E6 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:solid #E6E6E6 .75pt;\n  background:whitesmoke;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt\">\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:normal\"><b><span style=\"color:black;\n  mso-color-alt:windowtext\">Interviewers</span><o:p></o:p></b></p>\n  </td>\n  <td style=\"border:solid #E6E6E6 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:solid #E6E6E6 .75pt;\n  padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt\">\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:normal\">Sandra Lasagni &amp; Antoine\n  Lassauge<o:p></o:p></p>\n  </td>\n </tr>\n</tbody></table>\n\n<div class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;line-height:normal\">\n\n<hr size=\"2\" width=\"100%\" align=\"center\">\n\n</div>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:normal\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color:#0070C0;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">1. Description of the\ninterviewee’s scope, responsibilities, and activities<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\n\n<ul style=\"margin-top:0cm\" type=\"disc\">\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:normal;mso-list:l5 level1 lfo1;\n     tab-stops:list 36.0pt\"><b>Position and responsibilities</b><o:p></o:p></li>\n <ul style=\"margin-top:0cm\" type=\"circle\">\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:normal;mso-list:l5 level2 lfo1;\n      tab-stops:list 72.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">Country\n      Manager for the Czech Republic within the Europlasma/LFB group.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:normal;mso-list:l5 level2 lfo1;\n      tab-stops:list 72.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">Statutory\n      representative for two Czech entities: <b>Europlasma</b> and <b>Amber\n      Plasma</b>.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:normal;mso-list:l5 level2 lfo1;\n      tab-stops:list 72.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">Joined\n      the company in 2019 as COO of Europlasma; since the 2024 acquisition of\n      Amber Plasma and the 2025 reorganisation, he oversees both entities.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n </ul>\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:normal;mso-list:l5 level1 lfo1;\n     tab-stops:list 36.0pt\"><b>Geographical reach &amp; organisation</b><o:p></o:p></li>\n <ul style=\"margin-top:0cm\" type=\"circle\">\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:normal;mso-list:l5 level2 lfo1;\n      tab-stops:list 72.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">Operations\n      exclusively in the Czech Republic.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:normal;mso-list:l5 level2 lfo1;\n      tab-stops:list 72.0pt\"><b>15 plasma donation centres</b> in total: <o:p></o:p></li>\n  <ul style=\"margin-top:0cm\" type=\"square\">\n   <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:normal;mso-list:l5 level3 lfo1;\n       tab-stops:list 108.0pt\">3 Europlasma centres,<o:p></o:p></li>\n   <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:normal;mso-list:l5 level3 lfo1;\n       tab-stops:list 108.0pt\">12 Amber Plasma centres.<o:p></o:p></li>\n  </ul>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:normal;mso-list:l5 level2 lfo1;\n      tab-stops:list 72.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">About\n      <b>300 employees</b>, 95% working in operations (physicians, nurses,\n      medical and centre staff).<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n </ul>\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:normal;mso-list:l5 level1 lfo1;\n     tab-stops:list 36.0pt\"><b>Main missions and objectives</b><o:p></o:p></li>\n <ul style=\"margin-top:0cm\" type=\"circle\">\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:normal;mso-list:l5 level2 lfo1;\n      tab-stops:list 72.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">Lead\n      the integration of Amber Plasma into Europlasma/LFB processes and systems\n      (Harmonise HR, payroll, accounting providers, quality systems, IT\n      infrastructure, and back‑office processes)<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:normal;mso-list:l5 level2 lfo1;\n      tab-stops:list 72.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">Manage\n      operational challenges linked to the LFB crisis (temporary plasma\n      storage, redirection of plasma to Takeda instead of LFB France).<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:normal;mso-list:l5 level2 lfo1;\n      tab-stops:list 72.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">Ensure\n      compliance with inspections, quality standards, internal control\n      expectations, and corporate policies.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:normal;mso-list:l5 level2 lfo1;\n      tab-stops:list 72.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">Maintain\n      operational performance while dealing with significant resource\n      constraints.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n </ul>\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:normal;mso-list:l5 level1 lfo1;\n     tab-stops:list 36.0pt\"><b>Operational processes involved</b><o:p></o:p></li>\n <ul style=\"margin-top:0cm\" type=\"circle\">\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:normal;mso-list:l5 level2 lfo1;\n      tab-stops:list 72.0pt\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\">Purchasing</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\"> (suppliers, service\n      providers, renovations, construction works, marketing support).<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:normal;mso-list:l5 level2 lfo1;\n      tab-stops:list 72.0pt\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\">Finance\n      &amp; payments</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\">,\n      including validation workflows.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:normal;mso-list:l5 level2 lfo1;\n      tab-stops:list 72.0pt\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\">HR/payroll</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\">, integrated recently across\n      the 2 entities.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:normal;mso-list:l5 level2 lfo1;\n      tab-stops:list 72.0pt\"><b>Quality assurance &amp; inspections</b>.<o:p></o:p></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:normal;mso-list:l5 level2 lfo1;\n      tab-stops:list 72.0pt\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\">Cash\n      management</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\"> in\n      donation centres <o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:normal;mso-list:l5 level2 lfo1;\n      tab-stops:list 72.0pt\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\">Marketing</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\"> and donor‑acquisition\n      strategies (B2C activity).<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n </ul>\n</ul>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:normal\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></b></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:normal\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color:#0070C0;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">2. Categories of third parties,\nnature of interactions, corruption risks and existing controls<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:normal\"><b>2.1. Suppliers and Service\nProviders<o:p></o:p></b></p>\n\n<ul style=\"margin-top:0cm\" type=\"disc\">\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:normal;mso-list:l4 level1 lfo2;\n     tab-stops:list 36.0pt\"><b>Nature of interactions</b><o:p></o:p></li>\n <ul style=\"margin-top:0cm\" type=\"circle\">\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:normal;mso-list:l4 level2 lfo2;\n      tab-stops:list 72.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">Regular\n      use of external suppliers: accounting/payroll providers, construction and\n      maintenance companies, IT suppliers, marketing agencies.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:normal;mso-list:l4 level2 lfo2;\n      tab-stops:list 72.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">Tenders\n      are organised whenever possible, but in practice competition can be\n      limited (sometimes only 1–2 offers received).<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n </ul>\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:normal;mso-list:l4 level1 lfo2;\n     tab-stops:list 36.0pt\"><b>Frequency and business volumes</b><o:p></o:p></li>\n <ul style=\"margin-top:0cm\" type=\"circle\">\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:normal;mso-list:l4 level2 lfo2;\n      tab-stops:list 72.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">Frequent\n      interactions; some large‑value projects (e.g. centre renovations around\n      €100k).<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n </ul>\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:normal;mso-list:l4 level1 lfo2;\n     tab-stops:list 36.0pt\"><b>Corruption risks identified</b><o:p></o:p></li>\n <ul style=\"margin-top:0cm\" type=\"circle\">\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:normal;mso-list:l4 level2 lfo2;\n      tab-stops:list 72.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">Risk\n      of favouring a supplier, conflict of interest, or undue influence during\n      selection.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:normal;mso-list:l4 level2 lfo2;\n      tab-stops:list 72.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">Risk\n      linked to gifts or invitations that might create a sense of obligation.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:normal;mso-list:l4 level2 lfo2;\n      tab-stops:list 72.0pt\">Market structure sometimes limits competition.<o:p></o:p></li>\n </ul>\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:normal;mso-list:l4 level1 lfo2;\n     tab-stops:list 36.0pt\"><b>Controls mentioned</b><o:p></o:p></li>\n <ul style=\"margin-top:0cm\" type=\"circle\">\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:normal;mso-list:l4 level2 lfo2;\n      tab-stops:list 72.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">Threshold\n      at <b>€6,000</b> requiring at least a comparative offer.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:normal;mso-list:l4 level2 lfo2;\n      tab-stops:list 72.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">Validation\n      by senior management (Country Manager, CFO, Head of Operations).<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:normal;mso-list:l4 level2 lfo2;\n      tab-stops:list 72.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">Central\n      Finance involvement above certain thresholds.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:normal;mso-list:l4 level2 lfo2;\n      tab-stops:list 72.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">Documentation\n      of failed tender attempts when the market does not respond.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n </ul>\n</ul>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:normal\"><b>2.2. Regulatory and\nSupervisory Authorities<o:p></o:p></b></p>\n\n<ul style=\"margin-top:0cm\" type=\"disc\">\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:normal;mso-list:l2 level1 lfo3;\n     tab-stops:list 36.0pt\"><b>Nature of interactions</b><o:p></o:p></li>\n <ul style=\"margin-top:0cm\" type=\"circle\">\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:normal;mso-list:l2 level2 lfo3;\n      tab-stops:list 72.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">Regular\n      inspections of collection centres by health authorities<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n </ul>\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:normal;mso-list:l2 level1 lfo3;\n     tab-stops:list 36.0pt\"><b>Frequency</b><o:p></o:p></li>\n <ul style=\"margin-top:0cm\" type=\"circle\">\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:normal;mso-list:l2 level2 lfo3;\n      tab-stops:list 72.0pt\">Recurrent and mandatory.<o:p></o:p></li>\n </ul>\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:normal;mso-list:l2 level1 lfo3;\n     tab-stops:list 36.0pt\"><b>Corruption risks identified</b><o:p></o:p></li>\n <ul style=\"margin-top:0cm\" type=\"circle\">\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:normal;mso-list:l2 level2 lfo3;\n      tab-stops:list 72.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">The\n      interviewee reports <b>no direct exposure</b> in his long experience.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:normal;mso-list:l2 level2 lfo3;\n      tab-stops:list 72.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">Authorities\n      strictly refuse any benefit (even lunch or small refreshments).<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n </ul>\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:normal;mso-list:l2 level1 lfo3;\n     tab-stops:list 36.0pt\"><b>Controls mentioned</b><o:p></o:p></li>\n <ul style=\"margin-top:0cm\" type=\"circle\">\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:normal;mso-list:l2 level2 lfo3;\n      tab-stops:list 72.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">Systematic\n      presence of Quality Assurance representatives and the Managing Director\n      during inspections.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:normal;mso-list:l2 level2 lfo3;\n      tab-stops:list 72.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">Strong\n      internal culture: no invitations, no gifts.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n </ul>\n</ul>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:normal\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\">2.3. Donors (including the referral programme\n“Bring‑a‑Buddy”)<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\n\n<ul style=\"margin-top:0cm\" type=\"disc\">\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:normal;mso-list:l3 level1 lfo4;\n     tab-stops:list 36.0pt\"><b>Nature of interactions</b><o:p></o:p></li>\n <ul style=\"margin-top:0cm\" type=\"circle\">\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:normal;mso-list:l3 level2 lfo4;\n      tab-stops:list 72.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">Plasma\n      donation is the core B2C activity.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:normal;mso-list:l3 level2 lfo4;\n      tab-stops:list 72.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">Donor\n      referral bonus: ~80 EUR if a referred donor completes two donations.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:normal;mso-list:l3 level2 lfo4;\n      tab-stops:list 72.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">This\n      channel represents ~40% of new donors in some centres.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n </ul>\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:normal;mso-list:l3 level1 lfo4;\n     tab-stops:list 36.0pt\"><b>Corruption &amp; fraud risks identified</b><o:p></o:p></li>\n <ul style=\"margin-top:0cm\" type=\"circle\">\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:normal;mso-list:l3 level2 lfo4;\n      tab-stops:list 72.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">Donors\n      could attempt to influence staff to certify false donations in exchange\n      for payment.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:normal;mso-list:l3 level2 lfo4;\n      tab-stops:list 72.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">Possible\n      collusion between donors and reception staff for fraudulent attribution\n      of bonuses.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n </ul>\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:normal;mso-list:l3 level1 lfo4;\n     tab-stops:list 36.0pt\"><b>Controls mentioned</b><o:p></o:p></li>\n <ul style=\"margin-top:0cm\" type=\"circle\">\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:normal;mso-list:l3 level2 lfo4;\n      tab-stops:list 72.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">Automated\n      process requiring two real donations before payment.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:normal;mso-list:l3 level2 lfo4;\n      tab-stops:list 72.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">Timestamp\n      controls and daily bookkeeping of cash.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:normal;mso-list:l3 level2 lfo4;\n      tab-stops:list 72.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">Internal\n      audits and monitoring of which receptionist processes the most bonuses.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n </ul>\n</ul>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:normal\"><b>2.4. Plasma Industry\nAssociation / MoH<o:p></o:p></b></p>\n\n<ul style=\"margin-top:0cm\" type=\"disc\">\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:normal;mso-list:l1 level1 lfo5;\n     tab-stops:list 36.0pt\"><b>Nature of interactions</b><o:p></o:p></li>\n <ul style=\"margin-top:0cm\" type=\"circle\">\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:normal;mso-list:l1 level2 lfo5;\n      tab-stops:list 72.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">Collective\n      dialogue (Plasma Industry Association) with the Ministry of Health on\n      regulatory changes (SOHO regulation transposition, advertising rules,\n      donation frequency).<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n </ul>\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:normal;mso-list:l1 level1 lfo5;\n     tab-stops:list 36.0pt\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\">Corruption\n     risks identified</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></li>\n <ul style=\"margin-top:0cm\" type=\"circle\">\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:normal;mso-list:l1 level2 lfo5;\n      tab-stops:list 72.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">Corruption\n      of public agents / politicians to avoid regulation that can dramatically impact\n      the current way of operating<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n </ul>\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:normal;mso-list:l1 level1 lfo5;\n     tab-stops:list 36.0pt\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\">Controls\n     mentioned</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\"><br>\n     Limited budget, collective governance, legal oversight by external\n     lawyers.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n</ul>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:normal\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\">Overall main risks highlighted by the\ninterviewee<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\n\n<ul style=\"margin-top:0cm\" type=\"disc\">\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:normal;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo6;\n     tab-stops:list 36.0pt\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\">Purchasing</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\"> is considered the <b>highest\n     corruption‑risk area</b>.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:normal;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo6;\n     tab-stops:list 36.0pt\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\">Internal\n     fraud</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\"> linked\n     to cash management and referral‑bonus processes is a significant risk.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:normal;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo6;\n     tab-stops:list 36.0pt\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\">Authorities</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\">: exposure considered low to\n     negligible by Milan<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:normal;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo6;\n     tab-stops:list 36.0pt\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\">Legacy\n     Amber Plasma risks (pre‑acquisition)</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\"> impossible to fully evaluate; no known\n     cases.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n</ul>",
